{"tid":2298221,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"高質意粉/麵包黃店推介","createTime":"2020-11-24T02:04:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T04:56:27.000Z","uid":156688,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f6b66f46382656f142c8af2d945e65dc73fbc34b","tid":2298221,"uid":156688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T02:04:07.000Z","msg":"最近好想有一個諗法<br />\n好想食哂全香港鋪頭既意粉<br />\n咁當然係黃色經濟圈果啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最好就係小店<br />\n比較想關注小店多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n十八區都得架<br />\n<br />\n另外都好似好難搵到麵包店係黃<br />\n望黎望去好多都係山X，美心啲fd<br />\n所以想搵下有咩麵包店係黃<br />\n<br />\nThanks 各位巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"965b1f3903862a7acf62a9e8453389c7faafd6e4","tid":2298221,"uid":113784,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T02:13:25.000Z","msg":"享樂<br />\n新蒲崗/九龍灣"},{"pid":"227ca0181b572a21da84ff2da6840127b9966bbb","tid":2298221,"uid":156688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"965b1f3903862a7acf62a9e8453389c7faafd6e4","tid":2298221,"uid":113784,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T02:13:25.000Z","msg":"享樂<br />\n新蒲崗/九龍灣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T02:14:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔該哂 呢個星期會去試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86287a8b90a52f00287637c4fb27214800d97ca1","tid":2298221,"uid":57570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"965b1f3903862a7acf62a9e8453389c7faafd6e4","tid":2298221,"uid":113784,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T02:13:25.000Z","msg":"享樂<br />\n新蒲崗/九龍灣"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T02:15:09.000Z","msg":"同嚐味手作同一間？<br />\n係好食<br />\n不過係黃店？"},{"pid":"5d7185c90e34d97613deeb3b008227dce5c3b5c0","tid":2298221,"uid":18040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"